    <string name="about_summary">Version v1.0\n\nApp name: Clothing Classifier\n\nCore Features:\n- 50-category clothing recognition, offline ONNX inference, Material 3 modern UI\n- Settings take effect immediately: Language switch (Chinese/English), Performance priority (multi-thread), Theme mode (Follow system/Light/Dark), Result display density, Default camera selection\n- Camera features: Front/rear camera switch, Select images from gallery, Gesture focus (pinch zoom, double-tap focus)\n- History: Save results, Favorite function, Filter (category/confidence/time), Search, Share (text/image)\n- Others: Save images to gallery, Page transition animations, History management\n\nTraining &amp; Model:\n- PyTorch training → export ONNX, use ONNX Runtime inference in app\n\nModel Performance (Training):\n- Epoch: 27/100\n- Training Accuracy: 79.11%\n- Validation Accuracy: 60.90%</string>
